properties.areaDesc: San Luis Obispo County Central Coast; Santa Barbara County Central Coast; San Luis Obispo County Interior Valleys; Santa Ynez Valley
properties.headline: Dense Fog Advisory issued February 14 at 5:00AM PST until February 14 at 9:00AM PST by NWS Los Angeles/Oxnard CA
properties.description:
* WHAT...Visibility one quarter mile or less in dense fog.

* WHERE...San Luis Obispo County Central Coast, Santa Barbara
County Central Coast, Santa Ynez Valley and San Luis Obispo
County Interior Valleys.

* WHEN...Until 9 AM PST this morning.

* IMPACTS...Very low visibility will create dangerous driving
conditions.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Visibilities of one quarter mile or less
will create dangerous driving conditions.
properties.instruction:
If driving, slow down, use your headlights, and leave plenty of
distance ahead of you.

NWSheadline: DENSE FOG ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 9 AM PST THIS MORNING
